1100–1675 HP | Mitsubishi & Scania Marine
Engines in this range are designed for constant demand and long-hour operation. Each platform combines output, endurance, and fuel efficiency to keep fleets productive.
Each model is built for dependable propulsion under load and easy maintenance at sea or in port.

When deck crews change and maintenance standards vary, uptime still has to hold. Mitsubishi and Scania commercial marine engines in the 1000 HP class are built to run reliably, even when the people operating them can’t slow down.

These marine diesel engines meet EPA Tier 3 and Tier 4 standards without compromising output. Optimized combustion and advanced cooling systems improve fuel consumption and extend component life so operators burn less fuel, save more time, and stay compliant.
Every engine is backed by Laborde’s nationwide service network, stocked parts inventory, and responsive field support.
Not sure which model fits your vessel? Laborde’s engineering and sales teams can help you match power, performance, and footprint to your existing vessel or new build.

Laborde Products Marine Gensets: Power Generation You Can Rely On

paragraphs: For barges operating in the inland waterways, efficiency and reliability are critical. Our gensets offer a practical, long-lasting solution for providing continuous power to vital systems like navigation, cargo handling, and lighting. Built to withstand the unique demands of barge operations, these generators are designed for durability and reliability, ensuring smooth operations even in the most extreme conditions.
Keel-cooled gensets use the hull to release heat. They work well in shallow waters or areas with heavy debris, where other cooling systems might clog.

At Laborde Products, we specialize in marine diesel generators from trusted brands. We offer reliable Yanmar marine gensets, built for compact size and durability. We also supply FPT gensets, known for high performance and fuel efficiency.

Whether you need auxiliary power or a keel-cooled generator, we can help. At Laborde Products, we find the right solution for your fleet. Contact our team today to learn more about our marine diesel gensets or request a consultation.

text:
Engine Power for Every Journey
Laborde Products Delivers Dependable Marine Engines
Working day-in and day-out on the water is hard, honest work—you need marine engines and parts that are equal to the task. At Laborde Products, we understand the unique challenges and demands of marine operations because we live it everyday. Be it navigating inland waterways, operating a fleet of tugboats, or engaging in offshore exploration, our marine products are built to deliver reliable performance where it counts.
htmlExcerpt:
Engine Power for Every Journey

Laborde Products Delivers Dependable Marine Engines

Working day-in and day-out on the water is hard, honest work—you need marine engines and parts that are equal to the task. At Laborde Products, we understand the unique challenges and demands of marine operations because we live it everyday. Be it navigating inland waterways, operating a fleet of tugboats, or engaging in offshore exploration, our marine products are built to deliver reliable performance where it counts.

links.text: Tug Lucinda Smith Returns to Service with Mitsubishi Repower After Fire Damage →
Tug Lucinda Smith Returns to Service with Mitsubishi Repower After Fire Damage →

Inland 

Our engines and generators power a variety of vessels working throughout America’s inland waterways. Designed for durability and efficiency, they’re the dependable choice for operators who demand the best, without complication.

Tugboats 

In the tugboat industry, power and reliability are non-negotiable qualities. Our engines and parts help tugboats perform their duties effectively, whether it's docking, towing, or ship assist operations.

Fishing 

In commercial fishing, the livelihoods of dozens of individuals are at stake. As such, failure isn’t an option. Our engines and parts are rugged, reliable, and always ready to perform. You’ll be focused on your catch, not engine troubles.

Passenger 

Transporting passengers safely and comfortably is your priority. It’s ours, too. Our engines and generators power smooth sailing for ferries and tour boats, providing a reliable foundation for your passenger services.

Dredging 

Efficient dredging requires powerful, heavy-duty engines. Ours are built to withstand the rigorous demands of moving sediment and maintaining waterways, helping keep your operations on schedule and within budget.

Pilot 

Narrow channels and bustling harbors are daily challenges for pilot boats. That’s why they rely on precision and endurance in engines and parts. Our products guide every maneuver so that you can guide ships safely to their moorings.

Government and Defense 

We support government and defense operations with engines that deliver under pressure. Dependable and strong, they meet the strict requirements and high expectations of national service.

Offshore 

When you're miles from shore, you need engines and generators you can trust. Our engines power offshore operations with the endurance needed for oil rigs, exploration, and marine construction, so that even far from land, you're never without support.

For barges operating in the inland waterways, efficiency and reliability are critical. Our gensets offer a practical, long-lasting solution for providing continuous power to vital systems like navigation, cargo handling, and lighting. Built to withstand the unique demands of barge operations, these generators are designed for durability and reliability, ensuring smooth operations even in the most extreme conditions.
Keel-cooled gensets use the hull to release heat. They work well in shallow waters or areas with heavy debris, where other cooling systems might clog.

At Laborde Products, we specialize in marine diesel generators from trusted brands. We offer reliable Yanmar marine gensets, built for compact size and durability. We also supply FPT gensets, known for high performance and fuel efficiency.

Whether you need auxiliary power or a keel-cooled generator, we can help. At Laborde Products, we find the right solution for your fleet. Contact our team today to learn more about our marine diesel gensets or request a consultation.
